window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>When the fae invaded England with their armies and their magic, everyone felt like the world had changed overnight. It hadn’t. Especially if you were an Ironwood.</i></b></p> <p>While humans lost their knowledge of magic and monsters, the Ironwoods have been fighting against evil for centuries.</p> <p>While gods, fae, and magicians turned into tall tales and ghost stories, the Ironwoods became the stuff of legends themselves.</p> <p>Now, with Morrigan’s Generals free again in the world, the Ironwoods are going to need all their training—and their new fae brothers—to stop them.</p> <p><b><i>This box set collects all four stories of the Ironwood women as they get into plenty of trouble, slay their enemies, and find true love.</i></b></p> <p><i>Please note: </i>Ironwood<i> contains adult content, including violence, swearing, and steamy sex scenes.</i></p>"; 
